T1  - Inflorescence Damage by Insects and Fungi in Native Pili Grass (Heteropogon contortus) versus Alien Fountain Grass (Pennisetum setaceum) in Hawai'i
JO  - Pacific Science
SN  - 0030-8870
VL  - 55
